  "solution_html": "<div class=\"lc-section\"><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;color:var(--lc-success);\">✅ 完整解法</h3><pre style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,0.05);padding:12px;border-radius:8px;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;\"><code class=\"language-python\">from typing import List\n\nclass Solution:\n    def earliestFinishTime(\n        self,\n        landStartTime: List[int], landDuration: List[int],\n        waterStartTime: List[int], waterDuration: List[int]\n    ) -> int:\n        ans = float('inf')\n\n        for i in range(len(landStartTime)):\n            for j in range(len(waterStartTime)):\n                # 方案A: 先搭陸上設施 i,再搭水上設施 j\n                land_end = landStartTime[i] + landDuration[i]\n                water_start = max(land_end, waterStartTime[j])\n                water_end = water_start + waterDuration[j]\n                ans = min(ans, water_end)\n\n                # 方案B: 先搭水上設施 j,再搭陸上設施 i\n                water_end_b = waterStartTime[j] + waterDuration[j]\n                land_start = max(water_end_b, landStartTime[i])\n                land_end_b = land_start + landDuration[i]\n                ans = min(ans, land_end_b)\n\n        return ans\n</code></pre><h4 style=\"margin:16px 0 8px 0;color:var(--lc-primary);\">📖 程式碼走查</h4><p style=\"line-height:1.6;\">以<strong>範例 1</strong>(<code>landStartTime=[2,8], landDuration=[4,1], waterStartTime=[6], waterDuration=[3]</code>)為例:</p><svg viewBox=\"0 0 600 200\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:8px 0;\"><text x=\"10\" y=\"18\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">四種配對走查</text><rect x=\"10\" y=\"28\" width=\"135\" height=\"64\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"rgba(63,185,80,0.15)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-success)\"/><text x=\"77\" y=\"46\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-success)\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">i=0,j=0 方案A</text><text x=\"77\" y=\"62\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"10\">陸0結束: 2+4=6</text><text x=\"77\" y=\"78\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-success)\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"700\">完成: max(6,6)+3 = 9 ✓</text><rect x=\"158\" y=\"28\" width=\"135\" height=\"64\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.08)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-border)\"/><text x=\"225\" y=\"46\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">i=0,j=0 方案B</text><text x=\"225\" y=\"62\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"10\">水0結束: 6+3=9</text><text x=\"225\" y=\"78\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"10\">完成: max(9,2)+4 = 13</text><rect x=\"306\" y=\"28\" width=\"135\" height=\"64\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.08)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-border)\"/><text x=\"373\" y=\"46\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">i=1,j=0 方案A</text><text x=\"373\" y=\"62\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"10\">陸1結束: 8+1=9</text><text x=\"373\" y=\"78\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"10\">完成: max(9,6)+3 = 12</text><rect x=\"454\" y=\"28\" width=\"135\" height=\"64\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.08)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-border)\"/><text x=\"521\" y=\"46\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">i=1,j=0 方案B</text><text x=\"521\" y=\"62\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"10\">水0結束: 6+3=9</text><text x=\"521\" y=\"78\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"10\">完成: max(9,8)+1 = 10</text><text x=\"10\" y=\"118\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\">ans = min(9, 13, 12, 10) =</text><text x=\"285\" y=\"118\" fill=\"var(--lc-success)\" font-size=\"15\" font-weight=\"700\">9 ✓</text></svg><h4 style=\"margin:16px 0 8px 0;color:var(--lc-primary);\">⏱️ 複雜度分析</h4><table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:8px 0;\"><tr style=\"background:rgba(91,141,239,0.1);\"><th style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);text-align:left;\">指標</th><th style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);text-align:left;\">複雜度</th><th style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);text-align:left;\">原因</th></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\"><strong>時間</strong></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\"><code>O(n × m)</code></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\">雙迴圈枚舉所有陸上 × 水上設施配對</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\"><strong>空間</strong></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\"><code>O(1)</code></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\">僅用常數個變數追蹤當前最小完成時刻</td></tr></table><div style=\"background:rgba(255,200,0,0.12);padding:14px;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid var(--lc-warning);margin:16px 0;\"><strong>💡 Key Insight</strong><br><span style=\"line-height:1.6;\">銜接兩項設施的核心公式是 <code>max(前一項完成時刻, 下一項開放時刻)</code>,精確捕捉「等到兩者皆就緒才能出發」的語意,無需任何特殊資料結構。</span></div></div>"
